{"tid":2246477,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山度士與羅賓奴解約！月薪是3,194港元","createTime":"2020-10-17T06:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T05:01:14.000Z","uid":34571,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c37a38f162c6604f4e180f565a1132feb9881fb","tid":2246477,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:07:10.000Z","msg":"山度士官方宣佈和羅賓奴（Robinho）解除合約，而距離羅賓奴重返山度士，只是過了一週的時間。<br />\n<br />\n  山度士官方寫道：「山度士和羅賓奴達成一致，雙方同意暫停10月10日簽下的合約，以便讓球員專心於在意大利的司法進程中捍衛自己。」<br />\n<br />\n  根據巴西媒體的報導，羅賓奴之前由於2013年在意大利的一起強姦罪成立，面臨9年牢獄之災。而簽下羅賓奴讓山度士遭到贊助商的壓力，有一家贊助商決定解約。最終導致山度士決定和羅賓奴解除合約。<br />\n<br />\n  羅賓奴和山度士簽下的合約中，<strong><span class=\"red\">他的月薪是1,500里亞爾（約3,194港元）。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"32f729ab2683b9a98d4fb2a86c44e6e597cd3397","tid":2246477,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:10:15.000Z","msg":"雞姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d20ac6f9b63515e86ca97d1b9701c84e4b0101","tid":2246477,"uid":36894,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:39:18.000Z","msg":"快啲黎逃犯天堂做超級外援啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cc2b30e3d24f19a8f467d2c4b79e6da857bf29","tid":2246477,"uid":199454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"李志堅：我們可能簽入更多球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6317cab486fe9bedd11ac5ad2b76b577701536a0","tid":2246477,"uid":134997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26e1d0972c50dd978beaf9ef5110e9e4f2d2a655","tid":2246477,"uid":252993,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:46:47.000Z","msg":"黎香港啦，3000蚊，流浪都俾得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898f7f00384cd6cbd7b7975855fe2af6d53902d8","tid":2246477,"uid":252993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6317cab486fe9bedd11ac5